I've decided to stick with a thief at level 12, based on my recent 
experiences. (Remember, I was just getting comfortable with having 
100% experience level 10 characters when I left off.)

For the record, a pre-announcement, 'The Weakest Link' has 48 
teleporters.  The closest model to it would be 'The Cellars' in the 
tevfifty, except this time, there is an obvious pattern to where the 
teleporters take you.
